EBX® Data Exchange Add-on Version 3.0.2


See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
com.orchestranetworks.addon.adix
Classes and interfaces to call Adix import and export.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange
Classes and interfaces to call EBX® Data Exchange Add-on import, export and transfer data.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange.sql
Classes and interfaces to define mappings in EBX® Data Exchange Add-on SQL import and export.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange.transformation
Classes and interfaces to call EBX® Data Exchange Add-on transformation functions to convert data for import, export and transfer.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange.validator
Classes and interfaces to call EBX® Data Exchange Add-on import Excel, CSV, XML and transfer data service using validators.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex
Classes and interfaces to call the EBX® Data Exchange Add-on import, export and transfer.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.common
Provides the classes and interfaces used to supply a context for integrating EBX® Data Exchange Add-on services.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.common.generation
Classes and interfaces used to generate tables, fields and mappings for the XML and SQL import, export and transfer data services.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.configuration
Classes and interfaces to define specifications for the import, export and transfer data services.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.mapping
Classes and interfaces to configure mapping between source and target applications.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.result
Classes and interfaces to define a result when executing data import, export and transfer.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.transformation
Classes and interfaces to call EBX® Data Exchange Add-on transformation functions for the import, export and transfer data services.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.validator
Classes and interfaces to call EBX® Data Exchange Add-on import Excel, CSV, XML and transfer data services using validator.
com.orchestranetworks.addon.dml
Classes and interfaces to call the Dynamic data modeling service.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.adix: Provides samples of Excel/CSV import/export.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange: Provides samples of SQL/XML import/export and data transfer.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange.sql: Provides samples of defining mappings in SQL import/export.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange.transformation: Provides samples of XML import/export and data transfer using transformation functions.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dataexchange.validator: Provides samples of Excel, CSV, XML import and data transfer using validators.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex: Provides samples for creating the EBX® Data Exchange Add-on specification with new APIs.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.result: Provides samples for getting import, export and transfer result .

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.common.generation: Provides samples for generating tables, fields and mappings with new APIs.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.configuration: Provides samples for creating the configuration specification with new APIs.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.mapping: Provides samples for creating the application mapping with new APIs.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.transformation: Provides samples of Excel, CSV, XML import/export and data transfer using transformation functions with new APIs.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dex.validator: Provides samples of Excel, CSV, XML import and data transfer using validators with new APIs.

com.orchestranetworks.addon.dml: Provides samples of executing the Dynamic data modeling service.
